%div{id: dom_id(activity)}
  = image_tag user_avatar(activity.owner), class: 'circle'
  = link_to activity.owner.username, user_profile_path(activity.owner)
  created a new thread:
  - if activity.trackable
    = link_to activity.trackable.subject, forum_thread_path(activity.trackable)
    = local_time_ago(activity.created_at)
  - else
    But has since been removed
